column13: Overbank flow at control, multiple channels overland around station.
column14: @ Uncertainty: IVE method, 2-sigma value (2 x Uncertainty Value reported in *.ft File). @ 100% clear. Flood stage, overbank flows with multiple overland channels flowing around station. Not all flow captured at gauge. Braided flow through forest upstream from gauge, all flow appears to converge at road crossing approx 30m d/s from shelter. Regular QM wading section approx 50m d/s from shelter appears to capture all flows. Sensor reset at 1200 took a couple tries due to surge. Beyond max wade for QM - was able to go in from both sides to the center point but not quite reach for panel exceeding 10% in the middle. This QM is the best that it gets considering the flow conditions. Mid-section
